<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-5986] Streams State Restoration never completes when logging is disabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-5986</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When logging is disabled on a state store, the store restoration never completes. This is likely because there are no changelogs, but more investigation is required.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
